{"tid":111577,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又死1隻]江蘇男春節赴毛里裘斯度假　浮潛遇溺身亡","createTime":"2017-02-07T13:29:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-07T13:31:20.000Z","uid":32407,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6bebd25135f319a22a3a26865a78665de479cf48","tid":111577,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T13:29:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170207/bkncn-20170207060858728-0207_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170207%2Fbkncn-20170207060858728-0207_05011_001.html&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opScP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=fa8ca716\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170207/bkncn-20170207060858728-0207_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n江蘇南通一對夫婦於春節期間赴西非島國毛里裘斯旅遊度假，不料戴姓丈夫在淺水水域參加浮潛運動時遭遇意外，不幸遇溺身亡。據悉事發地屬於淺水海域，而戴男遇難的水域水深不足1.7米。目前當地警方仍在調查事件。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，戴男上月29日在當地海邊參加浮潛運動，但下海後沒多久，有人突然看到戴在水面漂浮，目擊者見狀立即救人，隨後將已失去知覺的戴男救到海邊，為他進行人工呼吸及心肺復甦，惟最終不治。事發現場的工作人員其後報警，由警方及法醫處理戴男遺體。<br />\n<br />\n有知情人士透露，出事後戴男的腹部發脹鼓起，符合意外溺水的特徵，但事發地屬於淺水海域，而戴男遇難的水域水深不足1.7米，且戴的身高逾1.7米，應該不會淹過其頭部。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a3bc29e905ee51755f076fa53040ba522c8ba68","tid":111577,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T13:30:23.000Z","msg":"老婆fat fat啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fadd043898f8e0266e8b4c0e10c663d3066470dd","tid":111577,"uid":20170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T13:30:34.000Z","msg":"睇見標題已正皮"},{"pid":"d99297b4028ab8bcf47c9faeb68bc4a720fb62f1","tid":111577,"uid":1149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T13:31:20.000Z","msg":"你啲post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}